nodes.text: Star Wars: The Unusual Suspects is an article about Sugi, Embo, Seripas and Rumi Paramita, the four bounty hunters who made their first appearance in the seventeenth episode of the second season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. The article shows concept art of the characters, commented by The Clone Wars' supervising director, Dave Filoni. It was published in Star Wars Insider 117.
